linux is an open source environment.It is very secure and Highly Customizable. There are different distros of linux like :
kali Linux which is used for Ethical Hacking and Penetration Testing 
arch Linux is highly Customizable and Extreme Control Over OS
 parrot OS is Like Kali Linux But It is more lightweight 
Fedora is cutting Edge Technology and latest features are in fedora
Ubuntu is used for every day use and has a user friendly interface
kali Purple is a distro used for defensive Purposes 
There are many more types of linux that are used all are used for two Purpose either to exploit your system or to defend your privacy from invaders
